Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,GUARDIAN. Stop browser AI from acting on internal LOGCOM apps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM use case: browser-based agent governance — protect CUI from\NComet, manus.im, and the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight active policies in the sidebar. Every event is screened against\Nthem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Synthetic browser intercepts stream into the GUARDIAN middleware — no\Ndata movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Per-event chat_json policy decision — agent class, confidence,\Nsignals, action.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.68,0:00:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Color-coded decisions: ALLOW · BLOCK · CHALLENGE_HUMAN · REDACT_PII.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Every decision is appended to a SHA-256 hash-chained audit log.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero call: a posture brief — BLUF, top exfil vectors, recommended\Ntightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cache-first. The brief is ready before the operator clicks. Three\Nscenarios pre-staged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code routes inside your accredited\Nboundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
